    "client_msg_id": "6542202f-c68e-4d5e-b39a-45297ab0f9e9",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Thanks. The underlying representation of the whole system is a reactive spreadsheet like model with nested spreadsheets.  For any property we can calculate the source in the spreadsheet and whether it is static or dynamic. That is used to patch the static values at runtime..",
